# ============================================
# Environment Variables
# ============================================
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your own values.
# NEVER commit .env to the repo.
#
# MCP connectors (Google Drive, SharePoint, Ahrefs, Meta Ads, Figma, Monday, etc.)
# authenticate through the Claude desktop app settings — no config needed here.
# Only add variables here that tool scripts need at runtime.
# ============================================

# Example:
# SOME_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
